All departures with the office that have been booked in Belgium will be cancelled, but holidaymakers will be able to receive a refund.
The Ghent court also declared the bankruptcy of three Belgian daughters companies: Thomas Cook Belgium, Thomas Cook Retail and Thomas Cook Financial Services.
